"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.10\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.10</span> 标题：水池（pool）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：בְּרֵכָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：brekah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam2:13\">2SA 2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam2:13\">2SA 2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam2:13\">2SA 2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam4:12\">2SA 4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:38\">1KI 22:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:17\">2KI 18:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:20\">2KI 20:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:14\">NEH 2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:15\">NEH 3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:16\">NEH 3:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:6\">ECC 2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song7:5\">SNG 7:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:3\">ISA 7:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa22:9\">ISA 22:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa22:11\">ISA 22:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa36:2\">ISA 36:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah2:9\">NAM 2:9</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מִקְוֶה, מִקְוָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：miqveh, miqvah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:19\">EXO 7:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa22:11\">ISA 22:11</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：κολυμβήθρα</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：kolumbēthra)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:2\">JHN 5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:4\">JHN 5:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:7\">JHN 5:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:7\">JHN 9:7</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：κρήνη</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：krēnē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir48:17\">SIR 48:17</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0418_pool.jpg\" alt=\"下所罗门池\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">下所罗门池 (© Liadmalone, CC BY-SA 3.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>水池是一个相对较大、露天的蓄水构筑物。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:19\">EXO 7:19</a> ：在这节经文中，希伯来文<em>miqveh</em> 可能是指一种特殊的蓄水池，或者更有可能是一个通用词语，重复前面的短语“埃及的水”。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa22:11\">ISA 22:11</a> ：在耶路撒冷的两道城墙之间建造的水池可能有两种用途：在围城期间储水，以及作护城河或灌满水的壕沟来阻挡攻击者。大多数译本都把这里的希伯来文<em>miqvah</em> 译为“reservoir”（“水库”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> ）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah2:9\">NAM 2:9</a> （《和》2:8）：这节经文的希伯来文本有一个问题，许多译本都是根据一个修订过的文本进行翻译的。水库中的水往外流，比喻尼尼微人从城里往外逃。因此，这节经文的前半部分可译为：“尼尼微如同一个水池，里面的水正在流失”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 直译），或“如水从裂开的大坝流出，居民也从尼尼微逃跑”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 直译）。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:2\">JHN 5:2</a> ，希腊文<em>kolumbēthra</em> 指的是一个周围有五个廊子的水池，水池四面各有一个廊子，还有一个横跨水池的中间。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:7\">JHN 9:7</a> 出现了同一个希腊文，但该处提到的水池要小得多，也简朴得多。这个水池已在耶路撒冷发掘出来。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
